{"tid":605860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"以事論事 點解要反普通話同簡體字","createTime":"2018-03-26T04:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T04:12:06.000Z","uid":136553,"like":10,"dislike":225,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e3f65ad152c579a8a9c43fa44ffae88757260cd9","tid":605860,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:44:23.000Z","msg":"柒下柒下咁<br />\n簡體字同繁體字都係古代存在既文字<br />\n簡體字係古代既草書<br />\n好多古文獻上面都有簡體字<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/124053_0c3c53f5f11d15ec7fdda2be20b70953.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F124053_0c3c53f5f11d15ec7fdda2be20b70953.png&h=ff36a991&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/26/124056_a84b1b6c51ad03a83e82b7677bd451bc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F26%2F124056_a84b1b6c51ad03a83e82b7677bd451bc.png&h=78549794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n關乜撚野「中共破壞傳統文化事」<br />\n<br />\n再講，廣東話亦都唔係香港本土語言<br />\n廣東話明明係20世紀廣東移民帶入黎既語言<br />\n香港真正既本土語言明明係圍頭話<br />\n普通話同廣東話、英文本質上無分別<br />\n都係外來語言<br />\n<br />\n另外，繁體字同廣東話都係中國人發明<br />\n點解講廣東話同寫中文就係本土？而唔係中國化？<br />\n本土定義係乜嘢？"},{"pid":"74df0430df5f8223ea8dcf9fd3a0e7de3c86f046","tid":605860,"uid":48083,"like":81,"dislike":3,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:45:38.000Z","msg":"以事論事, 我屌你老母臭閪仆街五毛"},{"pid":"f5eaf627c7b62d98af2ab67bdc26fba6ab40f9e2","tid":605860,"uid":119363,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"咁樓主有冇諗過，他日香港再冇人識講廣東話，咁香港，仲叫唔叫香港？"},{"pid":"dfc8b3a7f66f9837938347333351841b39e6c614","tid":605860,"uid":41292,"like":69,"dislike":1,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:48:20.000Z","msg":"我肯定每一個講話簡化字係從古從俗嘅<br />\n都無睇過簡化字總表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n從俗從古嘅全部都係第一表<br />\n而第一表得350個簡化字<br />\n多喎<br />\n全部簡化字係2235呀柒頭<br />\n<br />\n訓撚醒未"},{"pid":"