core":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"如果真正本土<br />\n應該全民講英文先係<br />\n好似ABC、新加坡人咁<br />\n點解會講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438d6043c685ef7b71e9c4c96b0b0d936bdce019","tid":605860,"uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:53:23.000Z","msg":"熡主舊post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蜀漢昭烈帝<br />\n&bull;<br />\n7 個月前<br />\n但元朝都係用緊漢制wor<br />\n同埋中國呢個概念又唔係得漢族<br />\n再者，成吉思汗個黃金家族分佈喺內蒙<br />\n外蒙係喀爾喀蒙古，都唔係元朝果班統治者<br />\n所以元朝係中國政權<br />\n1<br />\n12<br />\n#7<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/376755/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/376755/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"ad5eec14f710fd77cbafbb5a05d49aee2d88ac91","tid":605860,"uid":20241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"864fd1c59cfbae70a5bd6431cf81c6bb297f6725","tid":605860,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":23,"score":-23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"如果真正本土<br />\n應該全民講英文先係<br />\n好似ABC、新加坡人咁<br />\n點解會講廣東話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:53:34.000Z","msg":"呢個地方個個講廣東話所以咪講廣東話 咪係本土咯"},{"pid":"6669980d941c553e2d7ef071e1a82ef742b20a05","tid":605860,"uid":41292,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"樓主<br />\n以事論事嘅論係需要你讀下書先論<br />\n未讀書就論叫鳩up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51eb512754776a797f42459d6ca08a00d5072017","tid":605860,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5eaf627c7b62d98af2ab67bdc26fba6ab40f9e2","tid":605860,"uid":119363,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:46:08.000Z","msg":"咁樓主有冇諗過，他日香港再冇人識講廣東話，咁香港，仲叫唔叫香港？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T04:55:05.000Z","msg":"香港因為有錢先叫香港啫<br />\n無錢邊有人識"},{"pid":"80964f8a95134e7b15e46b6d821850f43a136567","tid":605860,"uid":45368,"like":5,"dislike":23,"score":-18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-